Class.Name: NSWorkspace
Class.Description: A workspace that can launch other apps and perform a variety of file-handling services.

InstanceMethods.Name: openURL:configuration:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Opens a URL asynchronously using the provided options.

InstanceMethods.Name: openURLs:withApplicationAtURL:configuration:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Opens one or more URLs asynchronously in the specified app using the provided options.

InstanceMethods.Name: openURL:
InstanceMethods.Description: Opens the location at the specified URL.

InstanceMethods.Name: openApplicationAtURL:configuration:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Launches the app at the specified URL and asynchronously reports back on the app's status.

InstanceMethods.Name: hideOtherApplications
InstanceMethods.Description: Hides all applications other than the sender.

InstanceMethods.Name: duplicateURLs:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Duplicates the specified URLS asynchronously in the same manner as the Finder.

InstanceMethods.Name: recycleURLs:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Moves the specified URLs to the trash in the same manner as the Finder.

InstanceMethods.Name: activateFileViewerSelectingURLs:
InstanceMethods.Description: Activates the Finder, and opens one or more windows selecting the specified files.

InstanceMethods.Name: selectFile:inFileViewerRootedAtPath:
InstanceMethods.Description: Selects the file at the specified path.

InstanceMethods.Name: typeOfFile:error:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the uniform type identifier of the specified file, if it can be determined.

InstanceMethods.Name: localizedDescriptionForType:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the localized description for the specified Uniform Type Identifier (UTI).

InstanceMethods.Name: preferredFilenameExtensionForType:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the preferred filename extension for the specified Uniform Type Identifier (UTI).

InstanceMethods.Name: filenameExtension:isValidForType:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns whether the specified filename extension is appropriate for the Uniform Type Identifier (UTI).

InstanceMethods.Name: type:conformsToType:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns a Boolean indicating that the first Uniform Type Identifier (UTI) conforms to the second UTI.

InstanceMethods.Name: URLForApplicationWithBundleIdentifier:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the URL for the app with the specified identifier.

InstanceMethods.Name: getInfoForFile:application:type:
InstanceMethods.Description: Retrieves information about the specified file.

InstanceMethods.Name: URLForApplicationToOpenURL:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the URL to the default app that would be opened.

InstanceMethods.Name: getFileSystemInfoForPath:isRemovable:isWritable:isUnmountable:description:type:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns information about the file system at the specified path.

InstanceMethods.Name: isFilePackageAtPath:
InstanceMethods.Description: Determines whether the specified path is a file package.

InstanceMethods.Name: iconForFile:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns an image containing the icon for the specified file.

InstanceMethods.Name: iconForFiles:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns an image containing the icon for the specified files.

InstanceMethods.Name: iconForContentType:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns an image containing the icon for the specified content type.

InstanceMethods.Name: setIcon:forFile:options:
InstanceMethods.Description: Sets the icon for the file or directory at the specified path.

InstanceMethods.Name: unmountAndEjectDeviceAtPath:
InstanceMethods.Description: Unmounts and ejects the device at the specified path.

InstanceMethods.Name: unmountAndEjectDeviceAtURL:error:
InstanceMethods.Description: Attempts to eject the volume mounted at the given path.

InstanceMethods.Name: desktopImageURLForScreen:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the URL for the desktop image for the given screen.

InstanceMethods.Name: setDesktopImageURL:forScreen:options:error:
InstanceMethods.Description: Sets the desktop image for the given screen to the image at the specified URL.

InstanceMethods.Name: desktopImageOptionsForScreen:
InstanceMethods.Description: Returns the desktop image options for the given screen.

InstanceMethods.Name: showSearchResultsForQueryString:
InstanceMethods.Description: Displays a Spotlight search results window in Finder for the specified query string.

InstanceMethods.Name: noteFileSystemChanged:
InstanceMethods.Description: Informs the workspace object that the file system changed at the specified path.

InstanceMethods.Name: extendPowerOffBy:
InstanceMethods.Description: Requests the system wait for the specified amount of time before turning off the power or logging out the user.

InstanceMethods.Name: requestAuthorizationOfType:completionHandler:
InstanceMethods.Description: Requests authorization to perform a privileged file operation.

InstanceProperties.Name: notificationCenter
InstanceProperties.Description: The notification center for workspace notifications.

InstanceProperties.Name: frontmostApplication
InstanceProperties.Description: Returns the frontmost app, which is the app that receives key events.

InstanceProperties.Name: runningApplications
InstanceProperties.Description: Returns an array of running apps.

InstanceProperties.Name: menuBarOwningApplication
InstanceProperties.Description: Returns the app that owns the currently displayed menu bar.

InstanceProperties.Name: fileLabels
InstanceProperties.Description: The array of file labels, returned as strings.

InstanceProperties.Name: fileLabelColors
InstanceProperties.Description: The array of colors for the file labels.

InstanceProperties.Name: accessibilityDisplayShouldDifferentiateWithoutColor
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether the app avoids conveying information through color alone.

InstanceProperties.Name: accessibilityDisplayShouldIncreaseContrast
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether the app presents a high-contrast user interface.

InstanceProperties.Name: accessibilityDisplayShouldReduceTransparency
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether the app avoids using semitransparent backgrounds.

InstanceProperties.Name: accessibilityDisplayShouldInvertColors
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether the accessibility option to invert colors is in an enabled state.

InstanceProperties.Name: accessibilityDisplayShouldReduceMotion
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether the accessibility option to reduce motion is in an enabled state.

InstanceProperties.Name: switchControlEnabled
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether Switch Control is currently running.

InstanceProperties.Name: voiceOverEnabled
InstanceProperties.Description: A Boolean value that indicates whether VoiceOver is currently running.
